        {
            "title": "高盛:若局勢緩和,股市將跑贏大盤,美元將走弱",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RRT_xg1M9RiRqWuUwZgKag--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7H00D_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 高盛在週五的報告中指出,如果地緣政治緊張局勢緩解,股市可能恢復近期的強勁表現,而美元可能走弱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Kamakshya Trivedi向投資者表示,宏觀市場繼續應對\"通脹過高、增長不足\"的局面,投資者正在評估伊朗衝突的影響以及能源衝擊可能持續的時間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛表示,\"央行定價已超過大多數模態上行估計的合理水平\",反映出市場對可能出現\"自1970年代以來最大規模能源供應衝擊\"的擔憂。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7b822455-9c9a-3f56-95d7-e1521bfb7a69-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然利率市場經歷了最劇烈的重新定價,但該行表示,股票、信貸和貨幣市場的波動\"較小\",投資者正在區分能源出口國和進口國。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛寫道,關鍵風險在於霍爾木茲海峽的中斷是否會持續,並迫使市場\"擔心嚴重的增長下行風險\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在這種情況下,\"將對股票和新興市場施加更大的直接壓力……並進一步推高美元\",因為投資者會轉向更安全的資產。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但該行強調,如果緊張局勢緩解,情況將相反。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"如果能夠實現更快速的緩和,符合近期的樂觀情緒,那麼全球股市跑贏大盤和美元走弱等先前的主題應該會恢復,甚至可能因近期事件而得到加強,\"該行總結道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B-%E8%8B%A5%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%E7%B7%A9%E5%92%8C-%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%B0%87%E8%B7%91%E8%B4%8F%E5%A4%A7%E7%9B%A4-%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%B0%87%E8%B5%B0%E5%BC%B1-124643144.html",
