        {
            "title": "高端持續布局東南亞市場 腸病毒71型疫苗向馬來西亞送件新藥審查",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nBip2aMB1S8YZL7oU986lA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/cc33c9b7428ecdd674602e1a3dea1225\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E7%AB%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%9E%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E8%85%B8%E7%97%85%E6%AF%9271%E5%9E%8B%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E5%90%91%E9%A6%AC%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9E%E9%80%81%E4%BB%B6%E6%96%B0%E8%97%A5%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5-113456604.html",
